text: Sergey Komissarov (born 3 December 1987) is a Russian competitive sailor. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's Laser class. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Russia Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Laser Category:Universiade medalists in sailing Category:Universiade bronze medalists for Russia Category:Medalists at the 2011 Summer Universiade
